name: **Inishdaugh**
description: Inishdaugh L915-850 Sheet 30 Flat walled garden but no remnant of house at N end. Camping in field provided. Some lazybeds. High clay cliffs to S. See how close it is to Bartraw Strand spit to the SW. The main channel for boats passing from the S part of Clew bay comes through this gap, the boats passing being a mighty sight.
